HEADWORD: Bondstone
<hw>Bond"stone`</hw> <pr>(b⟦ocr⟧nd"st⟦omac⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Bond</ets>,<pos>n.</pos>+ <ets>stone</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Masonry)</fld> <def>A stone running through a wall from one face
to another, to bind it together; a binding stone.</def>⟦br⟧
